{{obsolete}}
{{flavour|Converts the poison within a targeted creature into liquid flame, burning a poisoned creature from within.}}

'''Localized Ignite Poison''' is a monster-only spell. It functions like [[Ignite Poison]], but it only works against a single target, and has to beat their [[magic resistance]]. It cannot affect poisonous [[cloud]]s.

The following monsters could cast Localized Ignite Poison:

{{monsterlink|Salamander mystic}}

==History==
*Localized Ignite Poison was removed in [[0.18]].
*Prior to [[0.17]], Localized Ignite Poison also affected targets with poison-branded attacks, chunks, and potions of poison; this included player [[Naga]]s, [[Kobold]]s, green [[Draconian]]s, and players in [[Spider Form]].
*Localized Ignite Poison was added in [[0.14]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
